<br>
If you really like to solo using your summoned pets and it's important to you, however, then Zumaik's Animation is something you might want to look into getting (and hopefully for a better price, of course!).  Otherwise, I would just wait until you can use your level 62 pet, which is inexpensive, a huge improvement, and a pet that you can use for more than knocking down green mobs.<br>
